snippet.description:
The Android Hunter A Alpha Demo is now available to download for Windows 32-bit & Windows 64-bit! Head over to: http://androidhuntera.com/download/ to download the demo now!

You can find more information about the game at:

Don't forget to follow us! We're planning on updating more frequently as we near the release of the alpha demo!
